    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so you're saying the \"political agenda\" argument is mostly just people being partisan? that's interesting. i guess i'm just trying to figure out if there's any actual academic weight to those critiques, or if it's really just a disagreement over how much the law should change over time. i don't want to go into my seminar with a one-sided view.",
